<subSubSection id="83810992BB73FFC3FF2EF9F9FE52FDD1" lastPageId="8" lastPageNumber="215" pageId="6" pageNumber="213" type="diagnosis">
<paragraph id="CB245A19BB73FFCDFF2EF9F9FC73F9AB" blockId="6.[136,1452,1536,2031]" pageId="6" pageNumber="213">
<emphasis id="F9EF860BBB73FFCDFF2EF9F9FF49F98F" box="[136,250,1537,1562]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="213">Diagnosis</emphasis>
:—differs from 
<taxonomicName id="0C9B219ABB73FFCDFE14F9F9FDF8F98F" box="[434,587,1536,1562]" class="Agaricomycetes" family="Boletaceae" genus="Butyriboletus" kingdom="Fungi" order="Boletales" pageId="6" pageNumber="213" phylum="Basidiomycota" rank="species" species="brunneus">
<emphasis id="F9EF860BBB73FFCDFE14F9F9FDF8F98F" box="[434,587,1536,1562]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="213">Bu. brunneus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
in the small to medium basidiome with a smooth pileus, a thin stipe that develops reddish stains at the base and the isolated phylogenetic position.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="CB245A19BB73FFCDFF1BF9B0FC0FF9F6" blockId="6.[136,1452,1536,2031]" box="[189,956,1608,1635]" pageId="6" pageNumber="213">
<emphasis id="F9EF860BBB73FFCDFF1BF9B0FE86F9F7" box="[189,309,1608,1634]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="213">Etymology</emphasis>
:—‘ 
<taxonomicName id="0C9B219ABB73FFCDFEC4F9B0FE5FF9F7" authorityName="L. Fan &amp; H. Y. Fu" authorityYear="2022" box="[354,492,1608,1634]" class="Agaricomycetes" family="Boletaceae" genus="Butyriboletus" kingdom="Fungi" order="Boletales" pageId="6" pageNumber="213" phylum="Basidiomycota" rank="species" species="brunneoides">
<emphasis id="F9EF860BBB73FFCDFEC4F9B0FE5FF9F7" box="[354,492,1608,1634]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="213">brunneoides</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
’, refers to the similarity to 
<taxonomicName id="0C9B219ABB73FFCDFC86F9B1FC06F9F7" box="[800,949,1608,1634]" class="Agaricomycetes" family="Boletaceae" genus="Butyriboletus" kingdom="Fungi" order="Boletales" pageId="6" pageNumber="213" phylum="Basidiomycota" rank="species" species="brunneus">
<emphasis id="F9EF860BBB73FFCDFC86F9B1FC06F9F7" box="[800,949,1608,1634]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="213">Bu. brunneus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
